  "keyFeatures": [
    "CFDI 4.0 stamping for Sales Invoices and Payment Entries via TI Sin Problemas web service",
    "CFDI cancellation with SAT-compliant cancellation reasons and substitute document linking",
    "Automatic stamping on document submit with configurable Default CSD per company",
    "Hourly scheduled job to poll and reconcile CFDI cancellation status",
    "SAT catalog management (Tax Regimes, CFDI Uses, Payment Methods, Product/Service Keys, UOM Keys, Relationship Types)",
    "Custom compliance fields on Customer, Company, Item, Sales Invoice, Payment Entry, UOM, and more",
    "RFC and CURP validation utilities",
    "Custom PDF and email templates for stamped CFDI documents (premium feature)",
    "Addenda support for custom XML content in CFDI documents",
    "before_stamp_cfdi / after_stamp_cfdi document event hooks for extensibility",
    "Docker-based development environment",
    "Crowdin-backed Spanish (es / es_MX) translations"
  ],
  "publicApiSurface": [
